OL,4,Cthemselves stealing cars jailed
OL,6,FOn 4 September 2024, two masked men
OL,7,Fsmashed the window of a car parked on
OL,8,FDartford Heath. They punched the
OL,9,Fdriver in the face, dragging him out
OL,10,Fof the vehicle, before driving off in
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,FFour days later, another driver was
OL,14,Ftargeted whilst resting in a lay-by.
OL,16,FHe was punched in the face and struck
OL,17,Fwith a metal bar, then dragged out of
OL,18,Fthe car.
