OL,6,FMessages were found between himself,
OL,7,FTurner and a third, Billy Scamp , 19
OL,8,Farranging to meet up before the
OL,9,Foffences were carried out. Videos of
OL,10,Fthe cars stolen just minutes before
OL,11,Fwere also found.
OL,13,FLewis Turner, from Longbury Drive,
OL,14,FOrpington was charged with fraud by
OL,15,Ffalse representation.
OL,17,FScamp, from Eridge Green Close,
OL,18,FOrpington, was arrested on 3 October
OL,19,F2025. He was charged with two counts
OL,20,Fof robbery and handed a two year
OL,21,Fsentence, suspended for two years.
